* Alternatives

** Parsing

  - org-mode (https://hackage.haskell.org/package/org-mode)

    + list items can only be simple text.

    + not responsive to github engagement

    + supports output as minimal org source, but no pretty-printing

  - org-parser (https://hackage.haskell.org/package/org-parser)

    1. May be more complete than this library.

    2. Uses a templating system (ondim) for pretty-printing (exporting) to
       different formats.

  - orgmode (https://hackage.haskell.org/package/orgmode)

    + built on Parsec library

  - orgmode-parse (https://hackage.haskell.org/package/orgmode-parse)

    + built on Attoparsec

    + no  markup or block support

    + no pretty-printing

